26
00:01:50,872 --> 00:01:51,872
here either.

27
00:01:52,037 --> 00:01:55,050
Let us look into these
different topics.

28
00:01:55,437 --> 00:01:59,098
The first step is to analyze
the need for the product.

29
00:01:59,276 --> 00:02:03,438
What are the current technologies
that are being used, if there is no

30
00:02:03,627 --> 00:02:07,814
technology solution available at
all, what are the alternatives or

31
00:02:07,991 --> 00:02:12,366
substitutes that people have
found in our target context?

32
00:02:12,571 --> 00:02:16,883
We need to honestly define
what are the pros and cons of

33
00:02:17,067 --> 00:02:18,892
existing solutions.

34
00:02:19,064 --> 00:02:21,164
This requires a close collaboration

35
00:02:21,344 --> 00:02:23,669
with the people who
we are trying to help

36
00:02:23,857 --> 00:02:26,982
as well as other stakeholders.

