88
00:05:54,266 --> 00:05:58,916
As the goal is to maximize impact,
it would be great to be able

89
00:05:59,110 --> 00:06:03,110
to minimize the need for
maintenance and spare parts.

90
00:06:03,285 --> 00:06:08,698
We will see that in detail in
